### ============================================================================
### Branding de la Representacion Impresa por tenant -> /api/branding
### Plantilla (clasico | moderno | compacto | custom:tenant<id>), color de
### acento (#RRGGBB) y logo. Requiere modo multi-tenant (el tenant sale del
### token). Ver docs/plantillas-factura.md.
### ============================================================================

### Branding actual + plantillas disponibles
GET http://localhost:8000/api/branding
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c

### Cambiar plantilla + acento
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/branding
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "moderno",
  "accent_color": "#1A56DB"
}

### Limpiar el acento (color por defecto de la plantilla)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/branding
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accent_color": null
}

### Plantilla invalida -> 422
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/branding
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "no-existe"
}

### Hex invalido -> 422
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/branding
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accent_color": "rojo"
}

### Subir logo (multipart, campo "logo"; png/jpg max 2 MB)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/branding/logo
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----LogoBoundary

------LogoBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./logo.png
------LogoBoundary--

### Eliminar el logo (vuelve al logo global)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/branding/logo
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c

### Preview: clasico (base64 por defecto; no persiste nada)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/branding/preview
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "clasico"
}

### Preview: moderno con acento, PDF crudo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/branding/preview?format=download
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "moderno",
  "accent_color": "#1A56DB"
}

### Preview: compacto, factura NO electronica
POST http://localhost:8000/api/branding/preview
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "compacto",
  "no_electronica": true
}

### Preview con lo persistido del tenant (sin body)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/branding/preview
X-API-KEY: 7a775f6fb0d5ccab15cf149d2c60f15c
Content-Type: application/json

{}
